description: Demolition of buildings and erection of Part 5/Part 6/Part 7/Part 8 storey building comprising 4,059 sq.m of A1/B1 floorspace at basement and ground floor, and 142 residential units above (56 x 1 bed, 68 x 2 bed, 18 x 3 bed) and associated cycle storage, parking, refuse storage and landscaping.
